mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿，教下你啦傻仔，無大財團撐腰就記得有嘜屎橋都唔好做啦，廢事你學人做蚊型生意被人告返轉頭話你抄人侵權啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時你病發又無錢同人打官司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞脾都無得你食呀陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有病真係快d睇醫生啦，唔好周街害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8456878f6ed7dd7548ee62810de7c4db3d55de46","tid":1543344,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:28:36.000Z","msg":"入到黎<br />\n個個留言都無講自己創業，創邊一行<br />\n咁傾乜？無乜意思"},{"pid":"25df9da43be452b5072e8bfbf47270cf03cd0772","tid":1543344,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:31:23.000Z","msg":"辛酸史？仲未有得訓。<br />\n夠未？"},{"pid":"bf871ca7ed49e475a579e9381b23496695a4266e","tid":1543344,"uid":230502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:35:09.000Z","msg":"辛酸史就係有齊哂所有運行公司既工具，但唔知點搵客，用左一個星期諗方法去搵客，最後開業一個月回左本"},{"pid":"5102665f4179fc17a0498175c166353c1cb451b7","tid":1543344,"uid":154263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7e211ecd250e87f3f247c8b7e9f33843db58d3","tid":1543344,"uid":10451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:40:31.000Z","msg":"用三皮野開始，創業八年，死唔去又冇發達"},{"pid":"de68822475a94221e5a70de381d3d35ef0d2ff6e","tid":1543344,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:41:02.000Z","msg":"here.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W0rjHeB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW0rjHeB.jpg&h=9a2aaf52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足們:<br />\n我整咗個Butterfly分解教學比大家。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYoutube片: <a href=\"http://shorturl.at/aBNY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshorturl.at%2FaBNY4&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=5cdcfbc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://shorturl.at/aBNY4</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一方有難</span>  針<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">  八方支援</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山</span>  爆</strong>   <span style=\"color: gold;\">  各自努力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span>  黨<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">  時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求</span>  鐵</strong>   <span style=\"color: gold;\">  缺一不可!</span>"},{"pid":"2069d8ffe4347845801e03a53771f12b2efeb301","tid":1543344,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:51:02.000Z","msg":"有間純粹b2b串黎串去既公司，賺唔到乜大錢既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦冇咩野要搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勉強叫財務自由，食野同買game 唔洗計住計住咁，對我黎講夠晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係細個唔識死日日同d 大粒佬出去威既成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n代價係我21歲個時已經飲酒飲到個肝有事+尿酸過高<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4af4b8e3b8489ef9015841d44ae89872d590866","tid":1543344,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3183c826c4c939a3e8ddd9a2ed8f3c44319c55d","tid":1543344,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7cec68a706d1fef9562c8740571fdae0ff51314","tid":1543344,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"樓主不如你自介先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=